rformance for heavily-loaded SDN and has 10% higher probability to satisfy\nall (> 99.99%) the traffic after a single link failure for G-Scale topology\nthan Smore under the same flow entry limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Sep 2019 04:25:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-23"}
