 proposed in this paper effectively explains\nthe optical principle of dielectric microsphere imaging, gives optimized\noptical parameters, and has been applied in experiments, which is of great\nvalue for the practical application of dielectric microsphere nanometer\nmicroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Sep 2019 10:31:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-23"}
